title: Episode 292: F*ck Your FRENZ (Feat. Spice)
itunes:title: Episode 292: F*ck Your FRENZ (Feat. Spice)
description:
Dancehall Artist, Spice is here this week to promote her upcoming album “Ten,” as well as debuting her new music video for “FRENZ.” The ladies cover a range of topics including your friends sleeping with your partner, distractions during sex, and much more! Spice even gets real spicy when discussing her favorite sex position. Enjoy!
